kandi biyo bibera hano.

29
00:01:54,843 --> 00:01:57,909
Aka kadomo turakita 
akadomo ko "Kuringaniza".

30
00:01:59,154 --> 00:02:01,743
Uko umushinga unyura
mu byiciro bitandukanye,

31
